        <item>
            <title>領克 900 新車提前洩密，內地汽車博主違保密協議被追討 500 萬賠償</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/05/lynkco-900-leak/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=lynkco-900-leak</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/05/lynkco-900-leak/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 05 Jan 2025 05:52:52 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[lynk&co]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[領克]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1285207</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<div class="draggable sticky top-0 z-10 flex min-h-[60px] items-center justify-center border-transparent bg-token-main-surface-primary pl-0 md:hidden"><div class="no-draggable">汽車博主「陳震同學」近日就領克 900 新車提前洩密事件公開致歉，並向品牌方及業界解釋事件及處理方案，然而廠方因該博主違反保密協議而追討 500 萬元人民幣賠償。</div><div></div><div class="no-draggable">事件源於原計劃於 1 月 3 日晚上 8:30 發佈的影片，因工作人員設定錯誤，影片提前於早上 8:30 上傳，導致新車資訊提前洩露，嚴重影響品牌發佈會流程並造成經濟損失。</div></div><div></div><div><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1285215" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/screenshot_20250105_-694x395.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="395" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/screenshot_20250105_-694x395.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/screenshot_20250105_.jpg 1181w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div class="composer-parent flex h-full flex-col focus-visible:outline-0" tabindex="0" role="presentation"><div class="flex-1 overflow-hidden @container/thread"><div class="h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ckhev-79elbk h-full"><div class="react-scroll-to-bottom--css-ckhev-1n7m0yu"><div class="flex flex-col text-sm md:pb-9"><article class="w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]" dir="auto" data-testid="conversation-turn-9" data-scroll-anchor="true"><div class="m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5"><div class="mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]"><div class="group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn"><div class="flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3"><div class="flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow"><div class="min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5" dir="auto" data-message-author-role="assistant" data-message-id="80c91dcb-edf6-4a81-a22b-c8af0114e175" data-message-model-slug="gpt-4o"><div class="flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]"><div class="markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert dark"><p>陳震在影片中坦言，團隊已收到領克品牌的律師函，正積極處理後續問題。他表示，此事不僅影響品牌形象亦對同行帶來壓力，為此深表歉意。他補充，相關負責人員已經主動辭職，而新接任的同事將全面檢討及改進內部工作流程，避免再度發生類似事件。</p><p>根據相關消息，領克品牌依據保密協議向陳震團隊發出律師函，要求其在接獲通知後的 5 個工作日內，根據協議條款一次性支付賠償金 500 萬元人民幣（約港幣 HK$5,400,000）。</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></div></div><p>來源：<a href="https://m.sohu.com/a/845311678_115060/?pvid=000115_3w_a&amp;scm=thor.521_14-200000.0.0.&amp;spm=smpc.home.it-news11.3.1736042400015A5oXoZw_1467&amp;_trans_=060008_lym">sohu</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
